{"tid":1462082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你係旅客，無啦啦有班人阻你上機，你會屌阻你上機班人都係個政府？","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:10:23.000Z","uid":36775,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9dfed3a1590940255bb1fcd5033fb6306b47c924","tid":1462082,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先一定要脫離香港人呢個思維諗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n旅客本身係唔會對逃犯條例呢件事有充份理解<br />\n唔知邊面啱邊面錯，唔會知香港政府有幾離譜<br />\n如果無啦啦有班人阻佢走，第一印象一定唔好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>佢地會屌政府，不過對示威者仲不滿，屌你屌得仲甘</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴日塞機場係人太多行唔到，係間接令機場停止服務<br />\n而今日係主動阻人上機，已經係唔同性質<br />\n<br />\n咁佢地點會將個怨氣轉去屌政府，你地都已經幫777吸傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbab47c639dfe5b460a822ebc2bacea5882c988","tid":1462082,"uid":167277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"a4ebe2230de059fd88b7e78ff3b0f5e1e93121b9","tid":1462082,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"警犬扮架on9"},{"pid":"a9cf6030e9f3318a894eea781bd6678266c24daf","tid":1462082,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"無腦"},{"pid":"fad1a6492b16debfe41100ea829610b39041e343","tid":1462082,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:59:42.000Z","msg":"旅客係用來保護機場示威者，你要攪唔該出去搞警署狗屋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4d941fab581090e82e72816ab6e64a817ff7e49","tid":1462082,"uid":194177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"人多自然癱瘓到<br />\n切勿自己以肉體阻擋旅客<br />\n班機取消佢大條道理收賠償<br />\n但你阻到佢上唔到機係佢自己賠<br />\n會令佢地強烈反感<br />\n甚至回國後喪屌示威者<br />\n我地而家要爭取國際支持<br />\n有人試圖阻旅客<br />\n請溫和地解釋點解唔應該呢個時候咁做<br />\n<br />\n收工過緊嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣見"},{"pid":"9400a5e1e0e27c3babe830ebae8328b2d9ca57e9","tid":1462082,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"用香港人思維代入旅客點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得啖笑"},{"pid":"d047e6c907e56bc7a32af35cd72110ba7672ea78","tid":1462082,"uid":211724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15ddea63ad74844b7262668f9359aba6b816a849","tid":1462082,"uid":111955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"一定係警察做<br />\n尋日分化完唔work<br />\n今日又搵話題發大黎講<br />\n唔好比班狗發大件事，轉移視線<br />\n阻旅客上機係警犬，處理左<br />\n小問題，<br />\n我地返返主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c853c0672dbfbc4cc8a208c157aee5e0118f828","tid":1462082,"uid":246242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cba2997f841e9abb48fbf2bc6dfb7eb77ee2cb26","tid":1462082,"uid":16458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"88af5f9b1f180afa7be7463050cb97f0b8329bd1","tid":1462082,"uid":304663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"人多自然癱瘓到<br />\n切勿自己以肉體阻擋旅客<br />\n班機取消佢大條道理收賠償<br />\n但你阻到佢上唔到機係佢自己賠<br />\n會令佢地強烈反感<br />\n甚至回國後喪屌示威者"},{"pid":"92423ca46a645e954430a8e176ecca0fbd6f5cb4","tid":1462082,"uid":265675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy